#!/bin/vbash
# ============================================================
# vyos-portgroup-patch.sh
# PATCH for vyos-dynamic-menu.sh (v2.1)
#
# WHAT THIS ADDS:
#   1. Port Group Management (Create / Edit / Delete)
#      - Accessible from Firewall menu AND NAT menu
#   2. Smart port/address/network group pickers
#      - choose_port_or_group_field   (src/dst port fields)
#      - choose_addr_or_group_field   (src/dst address fields)
#      - All firewall + NAT rule builders updated
#
# HOW TO INTEGRATE:
#   Copy every section below into vyos-dynamic-menu.sh at the
#   positions marked by the "INSERT POINT" comments.
#   Then update the menu functions as shown at the bottom.
#
# STYLE: identical to vyos-dynamic-menu.sh v2.1 conventions
#   - tprint / tprintf / tread for all IO
#   - grep_cfg / cfg_set / cfg_delete for config access
#   - load_array for safe array population
#   - select_from_list for numbered menus
#   - cfg_begin / cfg_apply wrapping all mutations
#   - Hard-block safe-ADD: no overwriting existing items
